snippet.title: OpenRA Video Game Trailer
snippet.description:
OpenRA is a Libre/Free Real Time Strategy project that recreates the classic Command & Conquer titles.

This video game trailer is released with hindsight on the OpenRA Holiday Release - December 23, 2013.

Homepage: http://openra.res0l.net/

Alternative download link: http://sourceforge.net/projects/openra.mirror/

Music in video: 
Act on Instintct - original C&C (Tiberian Dawn) soundtrack
by Frank Klepacki
